Selector

 -> 4 different types
    
    o Element Selector
    o Class Selector
    o Id Selector
    o Universal Selector


-> colors
    o rgb(red, green, blue)
    o rgba - a:saturation
    o name
    o hex value
    o hsl(hue, saturation, lightness); 
    o hsla - a:saturation

-> quotation mark
   o visit unicode tale characters website

-> position 
   o absolute - take position only after mentioning parent class as relative
   o relative - impact parent class
   o fixed    - fixed element
   o sticky   - sticky for its particular class 

-> css Element
   o z-index to fix the layers of the component